Her deep knowledge of Kingwood and surrounding areas means she can offer insight into which communities are best for growing families, those who want nearby hiking trails, or who care most about an easy commute. Diane makes relocating less stressful by helping you every step of the way, so your family can feel settled quickly in a place you’ll love.

